    <description>this flow manages the following

1. creation of an invoice with mandatory attachement 
2. automatically sends the invoice to Business Central
3. Determines the correct approvers based upon the amount of the invoice
- &lt; 1000 â‚¬ : approver 1 and approver 2 from account record
- &gt; 1000 â‚¬
   - first approver &lt;&gt; CEO =&gt; approver 2 becomes the CEO
   - first approver = CEO =&gt; approver 2 is not changed
- checks if first and/or secord approver are &quot;out of office&quot;, if so approver is changed to delegeted approver
4. Starts the approval proces in Salesforce</description>
